For ASR1k related development we use one of the older release which is named mitaka. To use the mitaka release, follow these steps
In Devstack directory:
git clone https://github.com/openstack-dev/devstack.git
git checkout -b stable/mitaka origin/stable/mitaka
git branch
-you will see the following:
  master
* stable/mitaka
 To check if you are using the mitaka branch use
git branch.
The * next to stable/mitaka shows the branch we are on.
